。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"6e6bb38eece45ffb984ec77aaf4e9d67ad5b57f5","tid":2274609,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:06:59.000Z","msg":"洗咩懷疑<br />\n黑警毅進仔邊有專業可言"},{"pid":"6c6a948f62214ce61651bc58f5ab0cb147b236cb","tid":2274609,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"坦白講啊 管理大量長期失控嘅弱智人士嘅經驗邊個會夠狗隊高層多啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}